      "versionNonce": 7840,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777368698161,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\u2022 Authorised 1 Sep 2026; complaints accepted from 1 Jan 2027\n\u2022 David Lacey, inaugural Chief Scams Officer\n  (started 31 Mar 2026, ex-IDCARE founder)\n\u2022 World's first multi-party dispute resolution scheme for scams\n\u2022 A single complaint can implicate bank + telco + platform",
      "originalText": "\u2022 Authorised 1 Sep 2026; complaints accepted from 1 Jan 2027\n\u2022 David Lacey, inaugural Chief Scams Officer\n  (started 31 Mar 2026, ex-IDCARE founder)\n\u2022 World's first multi-party dispute resolution scheme for scams\n\u2022 A single complaint can implicate bank + telco + platform",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
