      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777368698161,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\u2022 Co-signed 7 April 2026 joint mobile-fraud alert with ACMA\n\u2022 Operates Investment Scam Fusion Cell (TPG, banks, govt)\n\u2022 Australians lost A$2.18B to scams in 2025 (+7.8% YoY)\n\u2022 Annual Targeting Scams Report",
      "originalText": "\u2022 Co-signed 7 April 2026 joint mobile-fraud alert with ACMA\n\u2022 Operates Investment Scam Fusion Cell (TPG, banks, govt)\n\u2022 Australians lost A$2.18B to scams in 2025 (+7.8% YoY)\n\u2022 Annual Targeting Scams Report",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
